   <text>
      <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_1834-01_page01.jpg"/>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="image1.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <name type="place" ref="./Placeography.xml#Edgeworthstown_IE">Edgeworthstown</name>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="1834-01-24"/>January 24, 1834. </dateline>
               <salute>
                  Sir
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
               I approve of the title page<lb/>
               for <title ref="./Workography.xml#Helen1">Helen</title>
               <lb/>
            </p>
            <p>I beg you will send the<lb/>
               first copy you can have<lb/>
               stitched together to<lb/>
               <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#North-Audley-Street-1_ENK">
                  <choice>
                     <orig>N<hi rend="superscript">o</hi>.</orig>
                     <reg>Number</reg>
                  </choice> 1 North Audley Street</placeName>
               <lb/>
               to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeF3">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. Lestock Wilson</persName>
               <lb/>
            </p>
            <p>Also I request that instead<lb/>
               of 9 copies as ordered in<lb/>
               my last to be sent to<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeF3">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. L Wilson</persName> you will<lb/>
               send her <hi rend="underline">ten</hi> - independent<lb/>
               of that stitched copy mentioned<lb/>
               above<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>I am anxious that you<lb/>
               should send the <hi rend="underline">revises</hi> of<lb/>
               the last sheets to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeF3">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. L Wilson</persName>
               <lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
               I am Sir<lb/>
               Your <choice>
                  <orig>Obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.</orig>
                  <reg>Obedient</reg>
               </choice>
               <choice>
                  <orig>Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.</orig>
                  <reg>Servant</reg>
               </choice>
               <lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName>
               <lb/>
            </closer>
            <closer>
               <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_1834-01_page02.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>R Bentley Esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                     <lb/>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back/>
